summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Ouroboros: Neural Emergence PostgreSQL migration. Backend APIs achieved 100% success rate (17/17 tests) with all PostgreSQL Duden-Register features working correctly. Frontend UI functional with minor modal interaction issues due to canvas overlay interference.

ui_bugs.issue: Canvas overlay intercepts clicks on tier panel buttons inside modal
ui_bugs.symptoms: Access Duden-Register button timeout - canvas blocks pointer events
ui_bugs.workaround: Modal buttons unreachable due to canvas z-index interference
